channel.title: Info on SYIpkpker, and others that crash your server
channel.description:
A guy name Rs2Crash registered here, and has this program that crashes servers on the Server Status by logging in on a lot of accounts. Nobody has found a complete way to fix this. Once people find out, your servers will be fine.
In the mean time, do not make any threads. There is enough and the staff does not like seeing all of that spam.
Thanks,
CopyRight

item.title: Info on SYIpkpker, and others that crash your server
item.dc:creator: @frugoo_scape frugoo scape
item.description:
@frugoo_scape wrote:

Here ill help you out. Configure you client.java not to let anyone in unless the letters in there username come from this array.
public String AllowChar[] = {“1”,“2”,“3”,“4”,“5”,“6”,“7”,“8”,“9”,“0”,“a”,“b”,“c”,“d”,“e”,“f”,“g”,“h”,“i”,“j”,“k”,“l”,“m”,“n”,“o”,“p”,“q”,“r”,“s”,“t”,“u”,“v”,“w”,“x”,“y”,“z”," "};

There you go. Saved you about an hours of work if you did not know how to fix it. My server is already blocking this little hole in our private servers.
